N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 211.14 - Position of judges and physicians

State Regulations

The judges shall be stationed at separate sides of the ring
as directed by the Commission, and the physicians shall be stationed at places
designated by the Commission. Notes
